Ranger Help for: slots
======================

SYNTAX:      slots
USAGE:       Anywhere.

SUMMARY:
Shows how many skill slots you have available and which skills
you can currently learn with their slot costs.

Slots are earned by advancing your guild level. Each guild level
grants between 4 and 20 slots (higher levels give more). You
spend slots to learn skills. Learning never consumes ordinary experience
or banked Ranger XP.

=============================================================================
